                    Bill Payment via Scratch Card
                </div>
                <p>Postpaid subscribers are used to paying their bills by walking in to the Warid business centers or franchises. Now customers have another way to pay their bills by using scratch cards.</p>
                <h2>Features</h2>
                <p>Bill through scratch cards can be paid in the denominations of Rs. 100‚ Rs. 250‚ Rs. 500 and Rs. 1000. Buy scratch card and credit your account instantly by entering the 16 digit scratch code. </p>
                <p>Available in two SMS-based options: </p>
                <ul>
                    <li> Pay your own bill</li>
                    <li> Pay your Family/Friend bill</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Benefits</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        Convenience of crediting
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Instant reactivation of suspended account for non  payments.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        Easy mode of payment accessible anywhere, anytime.(24/7  availability)
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        One scratch card for the convenience of postpaid &amp;  prepaid customers<br>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <h2>Mechanism</h2>
                <h2>To Pay your own bill</h2>
                <p>Step 1: Go to Menu and choose Write Message</p>
                <p>
                    Step 2: Type eb&lt;Space&gt;&lt;16 digits of scratch card number&gt;
                    Example: eb xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
                </p>
                <p href="#">Step 3: Send  to 129  </p>
                <p>To Pay your family/friend’s bill</p>
                <p>Step 1: Go to Menu and choose Write Message  </p>
                <p>
                    Step 2: Type
                    eb&lt;Space&gt;&lt;16 digits of scratch card number&gt;&lt; Space&gt;&lt;mobile #)
                    Example: eb xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx 032xxxxxxxx
                </p>
                <p>Step 3: Send  to 129 </p>
                <p>Note: For both options, SMS notification will be sent to subscriber mentioning receipt number after the adjustment has been made.</p>

                <h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>The scratch card number will be verified. If Scratch card number is valid‚ the amount of the card would be adjusted in billed amount of the subscriber. </li>
                    <li>If scratch card number is subject to invalidity, subscriber will be intimated via SMS. </li>
                </ul>
